lambdat\_threshold = fzero(@(lambda) zero\_eval\_lambdat(lambda,cc,wbar,F,r,y), initial\_guess);

Note that the initial\_guess in the above code represents the initial value you need to provide to the root-finding algorithm to start the search for the solution. You can choose an appropriate value based on the range of lambda and the problem's characteristics.

